commit.message:
Fix wiiuse linker flags in Makefile

The needed "-lbluetooth" linker flag was missing when enabling the "wiiuse" tilt feature, adding it fixes linker errors when compiling (tested in Ubuntu 22.04 LTS).

The needed "-lbluetooth" linker flag was missing when enabling the "wiiuse" tilt feature, adding it fixes linker errors when compiling (tested in Ubuntu 22.04 LTS).
